    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a streamlined, aerodynamic body and a glossy black exterior. The car features a sharply contoured hood, wide stance, and pronounced wheel arches, emphasizing its performance-oriented design. Its side profile reveals sculpted doors and a low roofline, typical of high-end supercars. The front end is characterized by a wide grille and narrow headlights, while the rear is compact with integrated taillights and a subtle rear deck. The wheels are large and sporty, complementing the aggressive styling. The overall appearance suggests a modern, high-performance vehicle built for speed and agility.",
